stopped or connection is not started.  &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14941170" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 2 Oct 2015 14:04:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 301e32d69552bc183fadee471c45a1717a6347f1 in qpid-jms&apos;s branch refs/heads/master from Robert Gemmell&lt;br/&gt;
